- Updated [generate_report](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/kaggle-arena/ScienceResearchAI/ResearchProAI_Template/src/generate_report.py#39-58) to merge local and web context.
- Refined the system prompt for strictly academic analysis.

### [ingest.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/kaggle-arena/ScienceResearchAI/ResearchProAI_Template/src/ingest.py)
